            "text": "<p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p><p>We're here to help! Whether you have a question about your order, our products, or anything else, the Franky Nutrition customer service team is ready to assist you.</p><p></p><p><strong>Email</strong></p><p>For general inquiries, order questions, or support requests, email us at <a href=\"mailto:support@frankynu.com\" title=\"Email Franky Nutrition Customer Support\">support@frankynu.com</a>. We aim to respond within a few hours during business days.</p><p><strong>Live Chat</strong></p><p>Need a quick answer? Use our live chat in the bottom right corner of your screen to connect with our team in real time during business hours.</p><p><strong>Phone</strong></p><p>Call us at <a href=\"tel:+17864421243\" title=\"Call Franky Nutrition Customer Support\">+1 (786) 442-1243</a> during our opening hours for direct assistance.</p><p><strong>Opening Hours</strong></p><p>Monday to Saturday: 9:00 a.m. to 6:00 p.m. (US Eastern Time)</p><p><strong>Our Address</strong></p><p>Franky Nutrition Inc.<br/>1007 N Orange St. 4th Floor, Suite #4390<br/>Wilmington, Delaware 19801, United States</p><p><strong>Before You Reach Out</strong></p><p>You may find answers to common questions on our policy pages:</p><p><a href=\"https://frankynu.com/policies/shipping-policy\" title=\"Franky Nutrition Shipping Policy\">Shipping Policy</a><br/><a href=\"https://frankynu.com/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"Franky Nutrition Return and Refund Policy\">Return & Refund Policy</a><br/><a href=\"https://frankynu.com/pages/payment-methods\" title=\"Franky Nutrition Payment Methods\">Payment Methods</a></p><p>We look forward to hearing from you!</p>"
